OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPupils stay home with      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fparents on Fridays, MPs    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ftold                       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Some pupils have missed school on      
OL,6, Fridays since the pandemic because     
OL,7, their parents are at home, England's   
OL,8, children's commissioner has said.      
OL,10,FThe number of pupils regularly missing 
OL,11,Fschool in England remains higher than  
OL,12,Fpre-Covid levels.                      
OL,14,FDame Rachel de Souza told MPs there was
OL,15,F"a huge amount" of absence on Fridays -
OL,16,Fwhen "mum and dad are at home" - that  
OL,17,F"wasn't there before".                 
OL,19,FThe government said it is providing    
OL,20,Fhelp for regularly absent children.    
